items.desc: India's biggest EDM festival, Vh1 Supersonic, is back and this time it promises to be Super Crazy! With a phenomenal line up of headliners like Sean Paul, Major Lazer, Alt+J, Incubus, Marshmellow and Hypnotic Brass Ensemble, and guest stars like Nucleya and Dillon Francis, this one's bound to be EPIC. Watch this space for some exclusive dope straight from the festival.
items.title: Vh1 Supersonic 2018

items.desc: After two successful seasons of India's biggest model hunt, here comes season 3 of India's Next Top Model. Thirteen girls will battle it out to win the coveted crown. The judges for this season are, style diva Malaika Arora, fashion photographer Dabboo Ratnani and supermodel Milind Soman.
items.title: India's Next Top Model S03

items.desc: Fantastic performances, epic gags and some truly well-deserved awards! The Indian Television Academy Awards 2017 brings together your favourite TV and film stars for a star-studded celebration of the absolute best on TV. Watch now!
items.title: Indian Television Academy Awards 2017

items.desc: Get set to be 'entertained' with Entertainment ki Raat! A bevy of talented artistes like Ravi Dubey, RJ Mallishka, Raghu Ram, Aditya Narayan and many more are setting the bar high with their outstanding acts and mic drop sessions. So what are you waiting for? Tune in and add a dose of entertainment to your weekends!
items.title: Entertainment Ki Raat

items.desc: A suave detective who solves twisted cases in a jiffy, Dev Burman is a man shrouded in mystery. This detective has a past that haunts him, a dead wife that some believe he himself murdered, and a romantic interest who goes from being a con artiste to a tantrik medium in a minute! Ready for the thrills and chills?
items.title: Dev

items.desc: Dropout Pvt. Ltd. turns the spotlight on a bunch of under-qualified underdogs, or shall we say the square pegs who just don't fit in the round holes?! What happens when these so-called 'rejects' face the biggest real-world business challenges? Can their dreams survive the harshest reality check ever?
items.title: Dropout Pvt Ltd

items.desc: The nation's first and only English singing talent hunt is back with a whole new action-packed season and this time it's India who will decide the winner.  What's more? The Stage is now open to solo artists, duos and groups, which only means that the music and the madness is going to hit a note higher than ever.
items.title: The Stage S03

items.desc: What happens when a new born baby is picked by an influential god-woman as the God's chosen one? Life takes little Devanshi on a path too demanding for a child. But now, at only seven, Devanshi is about to enter the biggest battle of her young life as destiny pits her against the deceitful Mata Kusum Sundari, the same god-woman who chose her as the temple's 'blessed child'. Can she change the mindset of people whose lives have always been ruled by blind faith? Can a 7-year-old expose the manipulative and evil god-mother who has used and abused her power over innocent devotees?
items.title: Devanshi

items.desc: Getting married once? Perfect life. Getting married twice, that too with two different girls, that too on the same day? Baap re baap! Watch Bakool and his masaledar marital life turn upside down when he accidentally gets married to Sheena and Jigna. How will he manage two wives without going absolutely crazy? We suggest you sit tight with your family and watch Bakool's hilarious misadventures!
items.title: Bhaag Bakool Bhaag

items.desc: The story revolves around two sisters, Simar and Roli, who get married to the sons of the Bharadwaj family. The young bahus are the ideal daughters-in-law, and will fight villians and demons alike to protect their familyís pride & honor. Full of the several supernatural twists and a whole lot of family drama, 'Sasural Simar Ka' is a must watch!
items.title: Sasural Simar Ka

items.desc: This season of Khatron Ke Khiladi is loaded with thrills, chills and a whole lot of excitement! Rohit Shetty is back, all set to transform the gorgeous terrain of Spain into a battleground for a power-packed set of Khiladis. So are you ready to root for your favourites as they feel the 'pain in Spain'?
items.title: Khatron Ke Khiladi S08

items.desc: Ek Shringaar Swabhimaan celebrates the courage and pride of a small-town single mother, Sharda, and the values and strengths with which she empowers her young daughters, Meghna and Naina. As different as chalk and cheese, the fiercely independent girls have only one thing in common, their undying devotion towards their mother. Facing several hardships in an orthodox society, Sharda has provided the best upbringing and education to her girls. But what happens when it's time to find matches for her highly educated daughters? A single twist of fate will change everything forever!
items.title: Ek Shringaar Swabhimaan

items.desc: The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?
items.title: Thapki Pyar Ki

items.desc: HDFC Life YoungStars2 is a unique digital talent hunt for tiny tots with tremendous talent! Mentored by experts, 16 little singers, dancers, actors and musicians will partake in an epic competition. Who makes the cut and whose talent shines the brightest? Watch to find out.
items.title: HDFC Life YoungStars2

items.desc: Gaano Ka Rafu Center is back with it's second season and it's going to be double the fun! Watch your quirky host Sahil Khattar in his NO NO Money Singh avatar as he dissects popular songs. And if that's not all, he also has celebrities for company who jump into this laugh riot. Watch it, only on Voot.
items.title: Gaano Ka Rafu Center S02

items.desc: The most anticipated event of the year is back as 30 gorgeous ladies compete for the most prestigious crown in the country. Join in as superstars Ranbir Kapoor, Alia Bhatt and Karan Johar celebrate beauty like never before.
items.title: Femina Miss India 2017

items.desc: If there's one award night all of tinsel town looks forward to it's the Golden Petal Awards! Join TV's biggest celebrities as they come together to celebrate the fantastic year gone by. The red carpet has been rolled out, are you ready for a night of fashion, fun and all things fabulous?
items.title: Golden Petal Awards 2017

items.desc: Golden Petal Awards is an award function to honour personalities for their incomparable contribution to the channel. Television personalities will be honoured under popular categories in the award function along with the most entertaining performances by your favourite TV stars!
items.title: Golden Petal Awards 2016

items.desc: All you Akshay Kumar fans better get ready because the trailer of Toilet - Ek Prem Katha is finally here. And if this first look is anything to go by, this one's already a blockbuster! So what are you waiting for? Catch the trailer now on Voot.
items.title: Toilet - Ek Prem Katha Special

items.desc: A new talent show that has no votes and no judges. It's time for the game changer to take over! On India Banega Manch, the street is the artist's stage and all they have to do is win the crowd. Every performer has a stipulated time limit to attract as many viewers possible. So are you ready to pick your favourites?
items.title: India Banega Manch
